Sohrahl is a binary star system with two inhabitable planets and one inhabitable moon. The system is a wide binary (about 2000 AU apart) with two suns Sahrs and Sion.



Rahl:{
	Rahl (orbiting the sun Sion) is the planet where humans evolved. Currently it is a nightmare landscape of post apocalyptic disaster.


}


Vahrs:{
	Vahrs (orbiting the sun Sahrs) is the 'paradise' planet where most of the human population currently resides.

}
